            <lg xml:id="TK1">
<l>akara mutala veḻuttellā māti</l>
<l>pakavaṉ mutaṟṟē yulaku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As the letter A is the first of all letters, so the eternal God is first in the world.</l>
            </lg>
